org.sxb.data.redis.support.collections

クラス DefaultRedisMap<K,V>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.sxb.data.redis.support.collections.DefaultRedisMap<K,V>
  • すべての実装されたインタフェース:
    java.util.concurrent.ConcurrentMap<K,V>, java.util.Map<K,V>, BoundKeyOperations<java.lang.String>, RedisMap<K,V>, RedisStore

    public class DefaultRedisMap<K,V>
extends java.lang.Object
implements RedisMap<K,V>
    Default implementation for RedisMap. Note that the current implementation doesn't provide the same locking semantics across all methods. In highly concurrent environments, race conditions might appear.
    作成者:
    Costin Leau
